From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 05/10] nickel: new-tab-page — custom Nickel NTP WebUI

Add a custom chrome://newtab WebUI for Nickel Browser that shows:
  - Nickel branding / logo
  - Privacy stats (ads blocked, trackers blocked today)
  - Quick-access to Privacy Settings
  - Search bar (DuckDuckGo by default)

The NTP backend is a new WebUI handler; the frontend is pure HTML/CSS/JS
under chrome/browser/resources/nickel_ntp/.
